# 12. Phase 11 — Search and Utility Flows

After the core screens are stable, build secondary UX flows.

## Possible flows

- global search UI
- new message modal
- invite user modal
- file preview modal
- user profile popover
- notifications drawer

## Rules

- only build what product currently needs
- use existing modal/drawer patterns
- do not invent new visual language

